title: Putin Exposed West’s Intentions and ‘Became Most Popular World Leader’
text: The Russian President knows perfectly how ‘to play the diplomatic card’ and ‘never make mistakes,’ according to an expert of Press TV. Vladimir Putin intelligently exposed the lie of the West regarding Iran's nuclear program and the false conflict against ISIL. ...
